--- !u!114 &90870610
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 90870609}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: b3084848c5897dd41b9239769188f1bd, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  npcName: JULIAN VANE
  conversation:
  - characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: Don't think we've met. Nice to meet you.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: JULIAN VANE
    sentence: Julian Vane. Artist. Max told me about the funding last week. Said
      the Institute was restructuring. It's fine, I've survived worse.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: You don't seem fine.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: 'JULIAN VANE '
    sentence: Because then he pulls out a university. A university with his name
      on it.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: 'JULIAN VANE '
    sentence: Max has been buying my work for fifteen years, all of it sitting in
      this collection. That collection goes into a permanent institution and suddenly
      my life's work is just his legacy.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: 'JULIAN VANE '
    sentence: Forever. In his building.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: Can he do that?
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: JULIAN VANE
    sentence: He bought them fair and square so yeah. Technically.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: JULIAN VANE
    sentence: Max doesn't steal things. He just makes sure everything ends up being
      his eventually.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: Did you know what he was announcing tonight?
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: JULIAN VANE
    sentence: I just had a feeling it wasn't going to be good.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: "It seems like he doesn't want to talk anymore.\r"
    isItalic: 1
  repeatLine:
    characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: "It seems like he doesn't want to talk anymore.\r"
    isItalic: 1
  hasTalked: 0
